WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.760
Now, generative plus AI, an AI that can generate as well, generate what?

00:07.760 --> 00:12.980
Generate text, image, code, audio, video, painting, art, anything it can generate, like

00:12.980 --> 00:13.980
charge deputy.

00:13.980 --> 00:17.520
When you ask something to charge deputy, you will get the answer.

00:17.520 --> 00:20.480
So it is generating new text for you.

00:20.480 --> 00:26.080
It's not that it is like this thing is written in any file and it is just fetching from

00:26.080 --> 00:27.080
that file.

00:27.080 --> 00:33.600
No, it is generating the new text for you based on your question, based on the context

00:33.600 --> 00:39.440
of that question because this model has been trained on a huge data set.

